# Lock golden / fixture files to LF on every platform. The byte-equal
# integration suite compares output bytes against these files verbatim;
# without this pin, Git's autocrlf would rewrite goldens to CRLF on
# Windows checkout and every comparison would fail by exactly two
# bytes per line — even though the implementation (which always emits
# LF via `sys.stdout.buffer.write(b"\n")` and `csv.writer(lineterminator="\n")`)
# is unchanged.
*.json   text eol=lf
*.jsonl  text eol=lf
*.csv    text eol=lf
